
    IN the year 2017, courts tried these cases that rocked
Celebville! 1. ANC – The
African National Congress has over the past few months been subject to high
court judgments, which nullified some of its provincial leadership structures,
most notably in KZN.2. Mbongeni Ngema
– The playwright was arrested in Sandton for threatening his friend with a gun,
allegedly for flirting with his wife. He was granted R1 000 bail by the Wynberg
